From: Hyperion Kernel Project <hyperion@kernel.local>
Date: Thu Mar 12 2026
Subject: [PATCH] docs/admin-guide: add Hyperion performance tuning guide

Adds a reference tuning guide covering the BPF/JIT stack, sched-ext
runtime scheduler selection, x86 instruction tuning, ZRAM multi-stream
compression, and the IPE integrity policy framework as enabled by the
Hyperion v2.2.2 kernel configuration.

The document is placed in Documentation/admin-guide/ alongside other
operational guides so it is shipped with the kernel source and
accessible via `make htmldocs`.

Signed-off-by: Hyperion Kernel Project <hyperion@kernel.local>
